data.description: Welcome to this inviting 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath condo situated on the top floor of The Village at Maplewood, an active adult community that exemplifies comfort, convenience, and ideal location. This third-floor residence offers a unique blend of modern living within a vibrant and welcoming environment.    As you step into the open-concept living space, you are greeted by abundant natural light streaming through large windows, creating an inviting and airy atmosphere. The spacious living room provides an ideal setting for both relaxation and entertainment, with a seamless flow into the well-appointed kitchen.     The master bedroom is a private retreat, boasting an ensuite bathroom for added convenience and a walk-in closet that meets all your storage needs. The second bedroom is equally charming and well-lit.    Enjoy your morning coffee or unwind after a long day on the private balcony, offering scenic views and a perfect spot for relaxation. The Village at Maplewood provides a host of amenities, including a fitness center, community pool, and landscaped grounds, ensuring a resort-like experience right at your doorstep.    This unit also comes complete with a dedicated storage unit conveniently located on the ground floor, ensuring that you have ample space for belongings without cluttering your living areas.    Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and entertainment options, this condominium offers the best of both worlds – a peaceful retreat within reach of the vibrant city life. With easy access to major highways, commuting is a breeze.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite 2 Bedroom, 1.5 Bath condominium at the Village at Maplewood your new home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the epitome of modern living!
